REQUIREMENTS:
	1. Python - http://www.python.org
	2. SysVInit - ftp://ftp.cistron.nl/pub/people/miquels/sysvinit/sysvinit-2.85.tar.gz

INSTALLATION:
	1. su
	2. ./install.py 
	3. Follow the on-screen instructions

WARNING: Forty-two is still alpha. At this moment, if offers no real new features over other init systems. This release is primarily for developers working on Forty-two and Pynux.
